  "remarks": "Member of the Upper House of the Parliament, appointed by Alexandr Lukashenka. General Director of the public TV channel «Stolichnoe Televidenie», author and anchorman of the TV programme «The picture of the world». This programme is an instrument of state propaganda which supports and justifies the repression of the democratic opposition and of civil society. Democratic opposition and civil society are systematically highlighted in a negative and derogatory way using falsified information. He was particularly active in this regard after the crackdown on peaceful demonstrations on 19 Dec 2010  and on subsequent protests.",
